title: Google Cloud SDK release notes feed

items.content_html: • Fixed an issue with gauth that occurred when running a command beforecredentials were created.

• Developer preview release of the Cloud SDK
  • Includes command line tools for:
    • App Engine
    • BigQuery
    • Compute Engine
    • Cloud Storage
    • Cloud SQL
  • Includes the new gauth tool for one time common authentication for all tools
